Turn any video into a beautiful boomerang, including videos from your gallery and share it to social media. (Instagram especially).

Features:
✓ Turn any video into boomerang.
✓ No Watermark.
✓ Intuitive and easy LIVE editor to make your boomerang.
✓ Trim videos.
✓ Choose speed.
✓ Choose loop count.
✓ High quality boomerangs.
✓ No restrictions on video length.
✓ Great for Instagram, TikTok and other social networks.
✓ No compression or distortion to videos in social media.

Boomerit Boomerang Maker will help you to easily create the perfect boomerang with the highest quality.
Create a boomerang either from the built-in camera or pick video from your gallery. Use the live editor of Boomerit Boomerang Maker and choose a specific segment of the video for your boomerang, change the speed, number of loops, and share it!

Boomerit Boomerang Maker premium subscription all remove all advertisements automatically.
